name: Portland State University EC314 Public and Private Investment Analysis
tagline: This is an engineering economics course that is tuned to the Portland State University University Studies requirements and has a much lower math requirement than other engineering economics courses.
body:
### Welcome to Public and Private Investment Analysis
I'm experimenting with making my syllabus and course work my open to others to use and share.  This is the very start.

* Students:  Feel free add issues and I will address.
* Other Faculty:  Fork this syllabus if you like, or make contributions.  If you do fork, please give credit where credit is due.

If you are just looking for a pdf of the syllabus, you can find it here (https://github.com/woodsjam/PSU-EC314-Syllabus/blob/master/WoodsEC314Syllabus.pdf?raw=true).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
